title: End of the Harvest (1998) DVD
description:

A young Christian is humiliated after he attends a college philosophy club meeting filled with atheists. The club mocks his attempts to prove the existence of God, and now the unprepared student is out for revenge. After finding a mysterious paper written decades ago, he tries to ambush the next meeting by telling the students when the world is going to end and how it&#039;ll happen.
